In San Francisco, so on the west coast, you sit on the steering wheel - with the task of being the first in New York.
The basic idea includes a number of interesting elements.
The entire route is divided into ten stages and into more than fifty single races.
This means that each race is performed on a different route and that the individual stages take place in different, sufficiently different and interesting environments.
