Miguel Cruz López, Head of the Unidad de Investigación Médica en Bioquímica (Department of Medical Research, Focus Biochemistry) at the Hospital de Especiliadas del Centro Médico Nacional Siglo XXI stated that an interdisciplinary team consisting of doctors, nurses, nutritionists and social workers was established.
